</LG>
<LG N="16">
<HEAD>16.</HEAD>
<L><HI>Fancy,</HI> thou fail'&s;t me, <HI>here!</HI> I feel thee <HI>weak!</HI></L>
<L>I <HI>feel</HI> thee <HI>&s;ink,</HI> beneath th' <HI>o'erpow'ring</HI> Weight!</L>
