<L>Thou fee'&s;t the humbl'd Pride of <HI>Nature</HI> wait,</L>
<L>Mankind! collected into Life! the <HI>Lowly,</HI> and the <HI>Great!</HI></L>
<L>And <HI>thus,</HI> th' <HI>Eternal Doom</HI> thou &s;peak'&s;t! the <HI>Sentence</HI> of their <HI>Fate!</HI></L>
<L><HI>'Come,</HI> my ble&s;t <HI>Remant!</HI> ye &s;elected <HI>Few!</HI></L>
